{"tid":1403991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(長期置頂)「滿貼十八區」教育工程文宣圖收集","createTime":"2019-08-04T01:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T16:13:19.000Z","uid":285413,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"173b1978fd7dcf11f975bc15b911142a786182f9","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"各位如果同我一樣對深藍廢老深惡痛絕，<br />\n請一齊加入<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins><br />\n自發「滿貼十八區」教育工程文宣大隊</ins>!<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">由於要貼滿全香港，等啲唔睇連登、唔睇fb、唔上網的人群，<br />\n返工又見到，放工又見到，等車又見到，拍拖又見到......<br />\n所以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家放圖上嚟</span></span></strong>，<br />\n等每區啲手足因應各區嘅情況(邊類資訊缺乏就增補缺漏)，自行download印製教育文宣</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">教化班愚民！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一個人係冇可能做得哂，<br />\n所以如果<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">每人做啲，應該唔洗好多錢(返工嘅用office部printer印，老師用教員室printer印，至於公務員，唔使我教你啦?) 有能力嘅就印A3彩色(自製banner當然無任歡迎啦)，冇乜budget嘅印A4黑白，甚至手寫都仲得</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要教學性文宣!!</span></span></strong><br />\n要當街上啲路人乜都唔知咁教佢老味呀！<br />\n要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">擺事實，講道理</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>大是大非面前，不容佢哋抵賴！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">我要全香港都係連登呀！！！<br />\n我要全香港都知發生咩事！！<br />\n唔好再喺連登圍爐喇，<br />\n<strong>要圍就圍大啲，<br />\n全香港圍爐！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(請自行睇返 please refer to<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[**但唔好推喇，有勇武手足因此標題唔開心，所以睇返個前因後果就好了]<br />\n勇武收皮啦!! 唔好再圍爐，冇人睇連登㗎喇!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403873</a>"},{"pid":"35c2332bab100ea33d6270843239a3b6f1f77853","tid":1403991,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:46:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5fb3879e1c89b724338fb1a0fc93948761848ea","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKtQT1T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKtQT1T.png&h=5ead967b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4afa781fa3c6485216dc1d134d478ec745c70c56","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5idRPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5idRPL.jpg&h=d97f70a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b23f6fe19bbaa21364d2626ad60e49775f7368","tid":1403991,"uid":54545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5fb3879e1c89b724338fb1a0fc93948761848ea","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pKtQT1T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpKtQT1T.png&h=5ead967b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"多口問句 兩個協會係咪同一個? 同埋有冇日期？"},{"pid":"c68b6d25e824db14e20b442a93a732db4af488fa","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:07:12.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手，我搵圖/整圖都好慢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果有儲開嘅畀啲貨出嚟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n搵圖嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記得問