"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:05:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27b91f2f0a3f96d03aa44c87db0839b85916b382","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n千真萬確<br />\n大陸武警混入警隊 - 馮睎乾<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435730\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435730</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗好耐，好多巴絲&amp;我都親身識家人的朋友係國安或知道哩件事，所以<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>而家香港係多咗一倍警力</strong></span></span>，畀啲狗輪流休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫大家整理咗少少證據:<br />\n-家人識人落嚟香港做國安<br />\n-大埔講普通話&quot;同志，這邊&quot;<br />\n-有條差佬衝，唔聽白衫呀sir指揮亂衝<br />\n-唔戴委任證(因為佢哋冇)，所以索性全部人陪佢都唔戴<br />\n-有記者影到前線武裝警戴眼鏡唔戴con,話香港警察唔畀咁著(自行睇返上面條link)<br />\n-裝備錯搭，左輪手槍呀，嚴重槍械全部出動<br />\n-唔識警例<br />\n-突然大量人手<br />\netc<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以其實等同暗出兵，如果大陸咁驚外國話佢出解放軍，我哋可以整段片(配不同語言字幕)再發送多國報紙話:<br />\n&quot;<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其實解放軍已出</strong></span></span>&quot;<br />\n然後圖文並茂列出證據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等到有更具體明顯證據時，例如:白警流出國安來港的文件，到時直情可落報紙廣告，國際譴責。"},{"pid":"fac974c1d3f3ce8d4da87a1dba83a92478105999","tid":1403991,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m1pUNmL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm1pUNmL.jpg&h=cab809d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfwcy1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjfwcy1L.jpg&h=7182d1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HKkwPz6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHKkwPz6.jpg&h=6cf86998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fv6HbOr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFv6HbOr.jpg&h=5b074efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http